{"ayat_mp3":"https://everyayah.com/data/Alafasy_128kbps/002284.mp3","arabic":"لِّلَّهِ مَا فِي ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَمَا فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِۗ وَإِن تُبۡدُواْ مَا فِيٓ أَنفُسِكُمۡ أَوۡ تُخۡفُوهُ يُحَاسِبۡكُم بِهِ ٱللَّهُۖ فَيَغۡفِرُ لِمَن يَشَآءُ وَيُعَذِّبُ مَن يَشَآءُۗ وَٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيۡءٖ قَدِيرٌ","bengali":"যা কিছু আকাশসমূহে রয়েছে এবং যা কিছু যমীনে আছে, সব আল্লাহরই। যদি তোমরা মনের কথা প্রকাশ কর কিংবা গোপন কর, আল্লাহ তোমাদের কাছ থেকে তার হিসাব নেবেন। অতঃপর যাকে ইচ্ছা তিনি ক্ষমা করবেন এবং যাকে ইচ্ছা তিনি শাস্তি দেবেন। আল্লাহ সর্ববিষয়ে শক্তিমান।","english":"To Allah belongs all that is in the heavens and all that is on the earth, and whether you disclose what is in your ownselves or conceal it, Allah will call you to account for it. Then He forgives whom He wills and punishes whom He wills. And Allah is Able to do all things","wbw":[{"bengali":"আল্লাহর জন্য","english":"To Allah (belongs)","en_t":"lillahi","arabic":"لِّلَّهِ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_284_001.mp3"},{"bengali":"যা কিছু","english":"whatever","en_t":"ma","arabic":"مَا","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_284_002.mp3"},{"bengali":"মধ্যে (আছে)","english":"(is) in","en_t":"fi","arabic":"فِي","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_284_003.mp3"},{"bengali":"আকাশ সমূহের","english":"the heavens","en_t":"al-samawati","arabic":"ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_284_004.mp3"},{"bengali":"ও যা কিছু","english":"and whatever","en_t":"wama","arabic":"وَمَا","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_284_005.mp3"},{"bengali":"মধ্যে (আছে)","english":"(is) in","en_t":"fi","arabic":"فِي","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_284_006.mp3"},{"bengali":"পৃথিবীর","english":"the earth","en_t":"al-ardi","arabic":"ٱلۡأَرۡضِۗ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_284_007.mp3"},{"bengali":"এবং যদি","english":"And if","en_t":"wa-in","arabic":"وَإِن","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_284_008.mp3"},{"beng